Privacy Policy
ADİOS YAZILIM BILISM SANAYI VE TICARET LIMITED SIRKETI as
Adios Games
has developed the
This App
application as a free service. This service is provided at no cost and is intended for use as-is.
This Privacy Policy is intended to inform users about our policies regarding the collection, use, and disclosure of personal information for those choosing to use our service.
By using
This App
, you agree to the collection and use of information in accordance with this policy. Any personal information collected is used to enhance and provide the service.
Adios Games
does not share your information except as described in this Privacy Policy.
Information Collection and Use
For an improved user experience, you may be asked to provide certain personally identifiable information. This information is stored on your device and is not collected by
Adios Games
. However, the application uses third-party services that may collect information for identification purposes.
Third-Party Services
Below are the third-party services used by the app. Please review their privacy policies for more details:
AdMob
Google Analytics for Firebase
Facebook
Unity
AppLovin
Log Data
In case of an error while using the app,
Adios Games
collects data through third-party services. This data, known as
Log Data
, may include your device’s Internet Protocol (IP) address, device name, operating system version, app configuration, timestamps, and other related statistics.
Cookies
This App
does not use cookies explicitly. However, third-party services integrated into the app may use cookies to enhance functionality and services. You can choose to accept or decline these cookies. Note that declining cookies may limit certain app functionalities.
Service Providers
We may employ third-party companies and individuals for the following purposes:
To facilitate the service;
To perform services on our behalf;
To analyze app usage and improve functionality.
These third parties have access to personal information only for these purposes and are obligated to maintain its confidentiality.
Security
Your trust in providing personal information is highly valued.
Adios Games
employs commercially acceptable measures to protect your data. However, no method of transmission or storage is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.
Links to Other Sites
The app may contain links to external sites. Clicking on such links will redirect you to third-party websites, which are not operated by
Adios Games
. We strongly recommend reviewing the Privacy Policy of these sites. We hold no responsibility for their content, policies, or practices.
Children’s Privacy
This App
does not target individuals under the age of 13, and we do not knowingly collect personal information from children under this age. If such data is discovered, it will be immediately deleted. Parents or guardians are encouraged to contact us if they believe their child has provided personal information.
Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. You are encouraged to review this page regularly for updates. Any changes will be posted here, and this policy will take effect immediately after being updated.
Contact Us
If you have questions or suggestions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at
support@adiosgames.com
